
** Modes

  - *passive*

** Server

  - proftpd
  - vsftpd

** VSFTP

  - Needs a inetd.conf entry and a ftp user.

  - /etc/inetd.conf

  <example>
    ftp stream tcp nowait root /usr/sbin/tcpd /usr/sbin/vsftpd
  </example>
  

  - /etc/vsftpd.conf

  <example>
    # Allow anonymous FTP?
    anonymous_enable=YES
    #
    # Uncomment this to allow local users to log in.
    local_enable=YES
    #
    # Uncomment this to enable any form of FTP write command.
    write_enable=YES
  </example>
